WEBVTT

00:04:57.724 --> 00:05:03.467
All these untouchables,
three women and two men,

00:05:03.467 --> 00:05:06.816
they agreed to come.

00:05:07.436 --> 00:05:13.075
I could recall that they had used 
the best of their clothes.

00:05:14.475 --> 00:05:16.740
They brought new utensils.

00:05:18.000 --> 00:05:20.339
They had taken baths 
hundreds of times

00:05:20.339 --> 00:05:23.300
because it was unthinkable
for them to do.

00:05:23.300 --> 00:05:25.944
It was the moment of change.

00:05:27.254 --> 00:05:29.702
They gathered. Food was cooked.